

INSTALL
-------------

cd to this dir.

run ./install install
or
run ./install uninstall


starting stoping
-----------------

#to start ...
sudo systemctl start puredata.service
sudo systemctl start coloroton.service


#to stop ...
sudo systemctl stop puredata.service
sudo systemctl stop coloroton.service


#see status ...
sudo systemctl status puredata.service
sudo systemctl status coloroton.service




debuging
-------------------------

#view logs. see what you see ...
sudo journalctl -u puredata.service
sudo jounralctl -u coloroton.service
